formula: Dirichlet g.f.: zeta(x-1)*zeta(x-4)Multiplicative with a(p^e) = (p^(4e+7) - (p^3+p^2+p+1)*p^(e+1) + p^2+p+1)/(p^7 - (p^3+p^2+p+1)*p + p^2+p+1).  [Mitch Harris, Jun 27 2005]
